section.section:
The notice shall contain:
the date, time, and place of the election;
a description of which employees are eligible to vote in the election;
notification that a list of the names and home addresses of employees eligible to vote will be provided to the participating employee organizations;
instructions on how employees can remove their addresses from the list in accordance with subsection (c)(2) of this section; and
any other information that, in the judgment of the labor relations administrator, is appropriate to convey to Commission employees.
